```plantuml
@startuml becloudway_serverless-data-pipeline

actor User
participant "Public API" as PublicAPI
participant "RetrieveXMLTrafficData" as RetrieveXML
participant S3
participant "TransformTrafficDataToJson" as TransformData
participant "PublishTrafficData" as PublishData
participant "Kinesis Firehose" as Firehose
participant "Kinesis Streams" as KinesisStream
participant "StreamProcessor" as StreamProcessor
participant "Kinesis Data Analytics" as KinesisAnalytics
participant "DynamoDB" as DynamoDB
participant "AlertSaver" as AlertSaver
participant "AlertSender" as AlertSender
participant "Flask API" as FlaskAPI
participant Slack
participant "PowerBiForwarder" as PowerBiForwarder
participant "CurrentSituation" as CurrentSituation
participant "CurrentAlerts" as CurrentAlerts
participant PowerBI

User -> RetrieveXML : Request Traffic Data
RetrieveXML -> PublicAPI : Get XML Traffic Data
PublicAPI -> RetrieveXML : XML Traffic Data
RetrieveXML -> S3 : Store XML Data
S3 -> TransformData : Trigger on XML creation
TransformData -> S3 : Convert XML to JSON
S3 -> PublishData : Trigger on JSON creation
PublishData -> Firehose : Publish JSON Data
Firehose -> S3 : Store Processed Data
PublishData -> KinesisStream : Stream to Kinesis

KinesisStream -> StreamProcessor : Process Stream
StreamProcessor -> KinesisAnalytics : Real-time Analytics
KinesisAnalytics -> DynamoDB : Store Analytics Results
DynamoDB -> AlertSaver : Trigger on new data
AlertSaver -> AlertSender : Notify Alert
AlertSender -> FlaskAPI : Send Alert
AlertSender -> Slack : Send Alert Notification

DynamoDB -> CurrentSituation : Query Current Traffic
CurrentSituation -> User : Return Traffic Data
DynamoDB -> CurrentAlerts : Query Current Alerts
CurrentAlerts -> User : Return Alerts

KinesisStream -> PowerBiForwarder : Forward to PowerBI
PowerBiForwarder -> PowerBI : Update Dashboard

@enduml
```